maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.orig: Lea, we must not enter this area with anyone else.
maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.text: Лея, мы не должны входить в эту область с кем-либо ещё.

maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.orig: Make sure to disband your party before you proceed.
maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.text: Распусти свою группу, прежде чем продолжить.

maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.orig: Lea, we must make sure to explore this part on our own.
maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.text: Лея, мы должны убедиться, что исследуем эту часть самостоятельно.

maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.orig: So it is time to disband your party.
maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.text: Так что настало время распустить группу.

maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.orig: Is it here?\. Is the entrance in this area?
maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.text: Это здесь?\. Вход находится в этой области?

maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.orig: Is there any way to \c[3]activate it\c[0]?
And you remember how to do it?
maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.text: И ты помнишь, как это делать?

maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.orig: It is alright, we will just try our best.
maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.text: Всё в порядке, мы будем стараться изо всех сил.

maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.orig: You have a look around and I will watch the logs.\. Maybe I can pick up something as well.
maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.text: Ты осмотрись вокруг, а я посмотрю логи.\. Может быть, я тоже смогу что-нибудь подобрать.

maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.orig: I am detecting some \c[3]tracking\c[0] in the logs.
Did you hear that sound, too?
It sounded like we did something right.
maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.text: Это звучало так, как будто мы сделали что-то правильно.

maps/forest/caves/path-11-maze.json/enti.orig: Let us look around some more.
Seems like we are getting closer.
